Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:14.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心里有了一丝预感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 今天一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:08.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该有些别的话可以对我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:18.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我钱放进去了但东西却没出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:22.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 因为这个相当旧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我想拍摄黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:38.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:43.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 夜晚变成蓝天的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚变成蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 再一会儿可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:10.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,西红柿豆汤？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:13.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说什么果汁出不来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在早上四点？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早上四点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:23.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拜她所赐 没能拍到好不容易才有的晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晴空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:32.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍天空真是不会腻烦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能会腻烦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有如此之多的变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,人也有变化不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:47.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你还问 我是来叫你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,班会要完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经是这个时候了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要急着去买东西对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个的话不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天已经买好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:21.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说是女孩子会反而会喜欢这种奇特的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:23.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾 差劲 没品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不懂得它的可爱之处…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你这自信是从哪里来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:39.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不要老做让人不舒服的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着 闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:49.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:56.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:04.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 小依总觉得有点别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 小依
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 真名总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 是姐姐 总是受到你的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:21.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我也是 姐姐承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:26.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里的话 一直陪着小依玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还是照样有礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真是姐妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,贫嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:37.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:42.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 今天顺道去了别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去了别的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个… 是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:06.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不喜欢蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我这边也有礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:14.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天是你生日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我比平常更用心 挑了又挑才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天这个我本来还蛮有自信的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你这个自信是从哪里来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:33.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在转换心情 来点上蜡烛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:40.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,相当大的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:58.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,听说教会的钟塔好像坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,教会？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 听说是要被拆掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:03.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:04.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拍一下回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 依人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,热衷于某事也要适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:58.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕不能吃 探病时间又没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为真的是太美了 忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐的生日对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不要这样么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:11.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以当作家人一起庆祝的只有依人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:12.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:19.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 什么时候看夕阳不都是差不多的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空又不会逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一样的两个天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无药可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:43.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生姜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:50.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么 生姜之类的事先准备好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名这个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让我稍微找容易寻找一点的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到真的下大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:34.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:37.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又出不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:16.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去便利店不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那里没有卖的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很好喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你不相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:35.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 这个拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,站远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:55.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 不要突然跑出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:59.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是觉得又伤到脚的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:21.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再下小一点就马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,做好上当了的心理准备哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,多买些储存起来会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不久就会停止贩卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很好喝的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 应该是不喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为天空会变得看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原来喜欢天空的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 昨天也在做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢那样做 拍摄不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有很多天空的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有兴趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也有一张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是一张而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的火烧云啊
